# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
tested with angular 11.2 and karma 6.3.2

### Is this a regression?
I think so yes. Never saw this error with ng9 + ivy and karma 5


### Description
As soon as a component property (string) is bound to an [outerHtml] dynamic attribute somewhere in its template, and is not empty, tests fail with the following error:

```console
NoModificationAllowedError: Failed to set the 'outerHTML' property on 'Element': This element has no parent node.
```
